profile: At Mr. Carpenter, your home or business is our work, and we take pride in both. Our dedication to providing high-quality craftsmanship and friendly customer service makes us a top provider of carpentry, maintenance, repair, and remodelling services across Prince Edward Island. The owner has been in the construction industry for over 25 years and is a master carpenter by trade. Mr. Carpenter prides itself on the following core values: Craftsmanship, quality, customer focus, love for the trade, and commitment.
